# Cloudflare Pages asset upload ignore file (copied verbatim into dist/ by
# Vite's publicDir copy, same mechanism as _headers next to it).
#
# Pack pmtiles (basemap.pmtiles, terrain.pmtiles) are served from R2 in
# production (see src/map/pack-base.ts) — sandia's alone are ~29MB/~80MB,
# both over Cloudflare Pages' 25MiB per-file cap, so they can't be uploaded
# to Pages regardless. They're still built into dist/ (dev/preview read them
# locally), just excluded from the actual Pages deploy here.
data/packs/**/*.pmtiles
